  "prompt": "What is Yelp?",
  "response": "Yelp is an online platform and mobile app that allows users to search for and review local businesses, such as restaurants, bars, shops, salons, and other services. Users can rate businesses on a scale of one to five stars and write detailed reviews about their experiences. Businesses can also create profiles, respond to reviews, and advertise on the platform. Yelp was founded in 2004 and has become a popular resource for people looking to find and evaluate local businesses based on crowdsourced reviews and ratings.",
